import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'my-first-c', templateUrl: './my-first-c.component.html', styleUrls: ['./my-first-c.component.css'] }) export class MyFirstCComponent implements OnInit { folders: string[] = ['my-first3-m (that contains a module to exporting this component content to application on browser module)', 'my-first-c (that contains the component files)']; constructor(){ } ngOnInit(){ } }
